  "title": "Retail Shop Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Retail Shop Sales Manager Recruitment</strong></p><p>We are seeking <strong>1 experienced Retail Shop Sales Manager </strong>to\njoin our team.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee daily retail shop operations and sales\n     management</li><li>Develop and implement sales strategies to achieve\n     performance targets</li><li>Manage inventory and product display, ensuring brand\n     standards are maintained</li><li>Achieve and exceed sales targets through proactive\n     engagement</li><li>Analyze sales data and propose improvement strategies\n     and marketing initiatives</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong> </p><ul><li>Minimum 3 years of experience in retail or sales\n     management</li><li>Excellent communication and customer service abilities</li><li>Bilingual in English and Chinese preferred, to engage\n     diverse customer groups</li><li>Positive, proactive attitude with the ability to thrive\n     in a fast-paced environment</li><li>5.5 days work</li></ul><p><strong>What\nWe Offer</strong></p><ul><li>A professional and collaborative working environment.</li><li>Opportunities for career development and advancement.</li><li>Competitive remuneration package</li></ul><p><strong>Compensation\n& Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Probation period (3–6 months):</strong> Base salary SGD$2,200–SGD$2,800 + high commission</li><li><strong>After probation:</strong>\n     Base salary SGD$2,800 + high commission</li><li>Attractive commission structure with significant\n     earning potential</li></ul><p>·       Supportive\nteam environment</p><h2>Additional Benefits (After Probation)</h2><ul><li>Full Attendance Bonus<strong> </strong></li><li>Annual Leave:<strong> </strong>14 days</li><li>Medical Leave:\n     10 days</li><li>Dental Subsidy:\n     $150–$300 per year </li><li>Education Materials and expenses: $300 - $500 per\n     year      </li></ul><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p><p><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time</p><p>Interested candidates are invited to\nsubmit their <strong>resume </strong>for consideration. Only shortlisted applicants will\nbe contacted</p>",
